---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Mail, Rocket, Github } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Blog Tech - About Me"
    description="Hola Soy Epadev te invito a descrubrir las últimas tendencias y avances en tecnologías de vanguardia."
>
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-10 pb-16">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">About Me</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-light dark:text-muted-dark">
                A little bit about my journey, my passions, and the purpose of
                this blog.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div
            class="mt-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-12"
        >
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 shrink-0">
                <img
                    alt="A professional photo of the author"
                    class="rounded-xl w-full aspect-square object-cover shadow-lg"
                    src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCsCgH9eHnTfvs6SITWyuipPL3fKY1PXhinCmaWDDXt0VfbfmH1S5MJOYp6Mwwm8bMigEfkexB-GDRWbKFEHft1uNR_C9g08RLBm9tjw52ERKMEtb3FjXHBGeho2Dpn-rPtNgxs6_oqoPPtFLhqvu8w6CpBfuygK70iKv_Z62Qy0HtUF_hY_2fQLcf1tm4fsScyz1O2QHY72n_JreNLyXhIOdeWtnZoOe4bsqO9kliVd4eDAaGwV6gHNc3t3x9Soorhb3aWG86ihWQ"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
                <div
                    class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-p:text-muted-light dark:prose-p:text-muted-dark prose-headings:text-on-surface-light dark:prose-headings:text-on-surface-dark"
                >
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Who am I?</h2>
                    <p>
                        I'm a passionate developer, writer, and lifelong
                        learner. My journey into the world of technology started
                        with a simple "Hello, World!" and has since evolved into
                        a deep fascination with building elegant, efficient, and
                        user-friendly digital experiences. I specialize in
                        front-end development, with a keen interest in modern
                        JavaScript frameworks and the art of creating beautiful,
                        responsive designs.
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">Why this blog?</h2>
                    <p>
                        This blog is my digital garden—a space where I can share
                        my thoughts, document my learnings, and connect with
                        like-minded individuals. I believe that knowledge grows
                        when it's shared. Here, you'll find articles on web
                        development, productivity tips, deep dives into new
                        technologies, and reflections on my personal projects.
                        My goal is to create content that is not only
                        informative but also inspires you to build, create, and
                        explore.
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">My Philosophy</h2>
                    <p>
                        I am a firm believer in the power of simplicity and
                        consistency. In both code and life, I strive for clarity
                        and purpose. I advocate for open-source, continuous
                        improvement, and the idea that the best way to learn is
                        by doing (and sometimes, by breaking things). This blog
                        is a testament to that philosophy—a work in progress,
                        constantly evolving as I do.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-16">
            <h3 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold mb-8">
                Connect &amp; Collaborate
            </h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <a
                    class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-primary dark:hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                    href="#"
                >
                    <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                        <Mail class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4
                            class="font-semibold text-on-surface-light dark:text-on-surface-dark"
                        >
                            Email
                        </h4>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-muted-light dark:text-muted-dark"
                        >
                            Get in touch directly
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a
                    class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-primary dark:hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                    href="#"
                >
                    <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                        <Github class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4
                            class="font-semibold text-on-surface-light dark:text-on-surface-dark"
                        >
                            GitHub
                        </h4>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-muted-light dark:text-muted-dark"
                        >
                            View my projects
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a
                    class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-primary dark:hover:border-primary transition-colors"
                    href="#"
                >
                    <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                        <Rocket class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4
                            class="font-semibold text-on-surface-light dark:text-on-surface-dark"
                        >
                            My Projects
                        </h4>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-muted-light dark:text-muted-dark"
                        >
                            See what I'm building
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
